    "description_long": "This is a sleek, modern sports car with a low, aerodynamic profile and a bold, muscular stance. The body is painted in a striking yellow-orange color, complemented by dark-tinted windows and black trim. The front features a wide grille with aggressive headlights, while the rear showcases dual exhausts and subtle sculpted lines. The car sits on large, five-spoke alloy wheels that enhance its sporty appearance. The side profile reveals a two-door coupe design with smooth, flowing contours and flush door handles. The overall design suggests high performance and urban sophistication, suitable for city streets or upscale neighborhoods.",
